name: Something (Jul._.li)
description:
Go through a maze of four elements to get legendary fifth one: THE SOMETHING.

Use WASD to control a little stick man. You may only go to a platform of the elements on displey. Try to collect something to get more points. Keep an eye on the timer.

Made in roughly 4 hours of designing and 3 hours of building for Trijam #184: The 3 hour game jam with the theme of "The Fifth Element".
